metadata.dcterms:title: University of Alberta Graduand Survey, 1992
metadata.dcterms:creator: Odynak, David
metadata.dcterms:description: The 1992 Graduand Survey was undertaken to assist the University of Alberta in its efforts to improve the quality of education received by students. The survey was conducted in June 1992 in conjunction with the University of Alberta's spring Convocation.
metadata.dcterms:spatial: Alberta, City of Edmonton, University of Alberta
